{
  "texts": [
    "More details about the simulation procedure can be found in the Methods section.",
    "Some simulation failures were encountered due to unstable initial configurations and fluctuations in temperature and pressure, which is common in workflows involving randomly generated starting configurations that may not always be physically realizable.",
    "To ensure sufficient sampling and accuracy, we performed simulations for each polymer with 5 replicas.",
    "Ultimately, MD simulation data was successfully obtained for 46 out of the 50 generated candidates.",
    "The four remaining candidates contained phosphinate groups, for which the necessary force field parameters were unavailable, preventing simulation of those systems."
  ]
}